# Onus Project Context

## Tech Stack

- Next.js 14 (App Router)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- shadcn/ui (dark theme)
- Supabase (mocked for now)
- Anthropic/Claude API (mocked for now)
- Framer Motion (page transitions)

## Folder Structure

```
src/
  app/           # Routes: page.tsx, onboarding/, dashboard/, history/, rewards/
  components/
    ui/          # shadcn components
    layout/      # Sidebar, Navbar
    dashboard/   # StatsRow, WeekView, CoachingCard, PaktCard
    onboarding/  # TierSelect, GoalBuilder, ContractSummary
  lib/
    mock-data.ts # All mocked data
    types.ts     # User, Commitment, Session, Penalty interfaces
```

## Design Tokens

- Background: #0e0e10 (primary), #131315 (surface), #1a1a1d (card)
- Accent: #c8f060 (lime green - CTAs, highlights)
- Text: #f0efe8 (primary), rgba(240,239,232,0.45) (muted)
- Danger: #f07070 (penalties, missed sessions)
- Border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07)

## Fonts

- Geist Sans: UI text
- Geist Mono: Currency, numbers, penalties
